You ready for your heart to explode? How about a video of Dolly Llama grooming a baby bunny? Alpacas are so incredibly curious and so nurturing. Dolly has been obsessed with all things baby since she herself was a baby, and I love watching all the precious ways that plays out. Wait till the end when Abbey comes to check and make sure Dolly is doing it right.

Всем доброго утра и отлично дня❤️ .
